{"tid":753414,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡利奧斯反擊批評：睇到人哋失敗就開心 我好同情你哋囉！","createTime":"2018-07-23T14:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T03:51:22.000Z","uid":4661,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2d23d6a85c48af0f0529db39428468af7d23c7fa","tid":753414,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180723/large/1532333881_726f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F1532333881_726f.jpg&h=22db17e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n效力利物浦的德國籍門將卡利奧斯，自歐聯決賽兩次嚴重犯錯，導致紅軍失落歐聯冠軍後，已經被無數球迷恥笑，甚至成為被紅軍或敵對球迷的攻擊對象。新球季還未開始，卡利奧斯在兩場熱身賽不論對英乙的燦美爾，或國冠盃對多蒙特均不斷犯錯，直接導致球隊失波，結果再惹來外界一連串攻擊。而紅軍最終亦下定決心，高價購入巴西籍門將艾利臣比加，取代卡利奧斯的正選位置。<br />\n<br />\n不過，卡利奧斯在周日戰罷多蒙特後，選擇Ig Story上反擊批評，稱：「對於那些看到別人失敗或受苦而感到高興的人，我非常同情你們。無論生命中發生甚麼事情令你感到憤怒或仇恨，我會為你祈禱那些情緒盡快過去，好事接踵而來。」<br />\n事實上，就連西班牙著名門將卡斯拿斯，今亦在Twitter上發推文為卡利奧斯發聲，希望外界放過卡利奧斯「這名孩子」，雖然亦獲得部份球迷支持，希望外界不要再給卡利奧斯壓力，否則只會犯錯不斷。但亦有部份球迷認為，卡利奧斯沒有強化改變自己的意識，反而認為是外界作出針對，而不對自己的犯錯作出反省，難道球迷沒有資格批評表現差劣的球員嗎？"},{"pid":"23b88099026f787afbbe9b7b59a180663675d301","tid":753414,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯：我屌你老母啦"},{"pid":"db85981db76f9ee41cdf0f5c290b5e45570a7fb4","tid":753414,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"靚仔大晒"},{"pid":"5c21fbf083eebf616b2323285caae16411017319","tid":753414,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"你咁廢唔笑你笑邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6868c2d1fc6945bdc8a6fda8c1bae7a3e8e9bc","tid":753414,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:53:34.000Z","msg":"連YNWA 都笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302811f0a536b718f81593aaa1ec556df019c078","tid":753414,"uid":30040,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"呢條友場上負責派學界膠，場下負責自拍自戀美顏相po上IG，<br />\n派完膠仲要賴3賴4，有冇諗過自己係需要改進牙？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27aa062d00594c4a8311f1244ae36b97eb4426f","tid":753414,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:06:49.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<br />\n無事就YNWA, <br />\n有事就DLLM!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb358584835926970bb7a1c1ec34356789fa8ca","tid":753414,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:16:40.000Z","msg":"Ddg 一開始到曼咪又係不斷派膠，有料嘅用實力塞住人把口，冇料嘅上Twitter 叫人收聲"},{"pid":"9e771f73a002bc503244802a620dc43347cd7274","tid":753414,"uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"米勞列都未出聲，你twitter就咁多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1e58f666cd954d7d18bee79b14f549a5dc3954","tid":753414,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailystar.co.uk/sport/football/718283/Liverpool-news-Loris-Karius-goalkeeper-errors-Borussia-Dortmund-fans-video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailystar.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F718283%2FLiverpool-news-Loris-Karius-goalkeeper-errors-Borussia-Dortmund-fans-video&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e3a433cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailystar.co.uk/sport/football/718283/Liverpool-news-Loris-Karius-goalkeeper-errors-Borussia-Dortmund-fans-video</a><br />\n<br />\n原來有球直頭好似踢街場咁 亂咁出迎 然後清唔到個波踢左比人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/